{"product_id":"dry-eye-comfort-3-bottles","title":"Eye Comfort 3 Bottles","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThis 3-bottle value bundle contains 180 softgels, or 90 days of suggested use.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEyetamins® by OPTASE® Eye Comfort™ is an omega-based eye supplement formulated to support moisture balance and eye comfort from within. The plant-based softgels fit easily into a daily routine, with a vegan, non GMO formula designed to align with a simple and consistent eye health routine.\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003eEyetamins® by OPTASE® is part of the OPTASE® Eye Care System. OPTASE® develops science-led, preservative-free eye care products with eye\u003cbr\u003especialists, with an eyecare routine that includes Heat, Cleanse, Hydrate, and Supplement to support comfort, hygiene, hydration, and nutrition.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003eAt the core of the formula is organic sea buckthorn oil blend. The oil is included to support moisture balance and day-to-day comfort for eyes prone to dryness. Each serving (2 softgels) provides 800 mg fruit oil extract plus 200 mg seed oil. Sea buckthorn is a naturally rich source of vegan Omega-7. The Omega-7 formula works to support healthy tear production and moisture balance from within as part of long-term daily support. If you want omega nutrition but prefer to avoid fish oil, Eye Comfort™ offers a modern plant-based alternative with no fishy aftertaste.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003eThe plant-based softgels fit easily into a daily routine, with a vegan, non-GMO formula designed to align with a simple and consistent eye health routine.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-olk-copy-source=\"MessageBody\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTake two (2) easy-to-swallow softgels once or twice daily with meals as directed for a simple habit that supports consistency and delivers well-tolerated, moisture support everyday.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eIngredients\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOrganic Sea Buckthorn Oil Blend, Modified Food Starch, Glycerin, Sorbitol, Carrageenan, Water\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Eyetamins, Inc.","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":40248059002937,"sku":"FRET-DE-Comfort60x3","price":104.85,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0600\/4903\/1225\/files\/2026_March_EC_3_Bottles.png?v=1773355285","url":"https:\/\/eyetamins.co\/products\/dry-eye-comfort-3-bottles","provider":"Eyetamins","version":"1.0","type":"link"}